<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/application.css">
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Pontano+Sans' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:900,300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>

<div id="header-text">PROBLEM CHILD</div>

<body>
  <div id="bg">
    <img src="/assets/02_app_background_image.jpg" alt="">
  </div>
  <div class="story">
    <p>Wait… we have 500,000 users. We only entered 13!</p>
    </div>

  <div class="lesson">
    <span class="lesson-instructions">
      <div class="browser-mockup">
            <p>How long is it going to take to enter all 500,000 users? Wait… what if more users sign up while we are spending our time writing all of our usernames into PROBLEM CHILD? Wait… What if someone changes their username? Why didn’t I just take that Google offer?!<br><br>
            There's got to be a better way!</p>

            <span class="lesson-buttons">
              <form action="/001_variables/06_question" method="get">
                <input type="submit" id="better-way-button" value="Take me to the better way!">
              </form>
            </span>
        </div>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="text-editor">
    <div class="window">
      <div class="window-titlebar">
        <span class="window-buttons">
          <span class="window-button window-button-close"></span>
          <span class="window-button window-button-hide"></span>
          <span class="window-button window-button-full"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="window-title">Code editor</span>
      </div>
      <div class="window-content">
        <ol class="code">
          <li class="line comment"># Welcome to PROBLEM CHILD</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_1 = '<%= @user.name %>'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_2 = 'Mom'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_3 = 'Jamie'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_4 = 'Oprah'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_5 = 'Matt'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_6 = 'Sarah'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_7 = 'Steph'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_8 = 'George'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_9 = 'Gabi'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_10 = 'Tyler'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_11 = 'Ronaldo'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_12 = 'Jacques'</li>
          <li class="line comment">user_13 = 'Avi'</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="repl">
    <p id="repl-text">|1.9.3-p545| |ruby-2.2.0|  <%=@user.name%>-MacBook-Air in ~problem_child.rb <br>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
